text: Château de Drulingen Château de Drulingen is a château in Drulingen, Bas-Rhin, Alsace, France. The building was built in 1816 by Jean Schmidt (1775-1844) upon his return from the Napoleonic wars. It became a monument historique on 16 July 1987. ==References== Drulingen Category:Monuments historiques of Bas- Rhin Category:Houses completed in 1816 Category:1816 establishments in France
